<reference id="steps-informal" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><xmlelement>steps-informal</xmlelement></title>
<shortdesc>The <xmlelement>steps-informal</xmlelement> element contains a set of informal steps.
        Informal steps do not follow a strict content model; a paragraph might describe more than
        one step, or a paragraph might combine procedural information along with other
        information.</shortdesc>
