<example id="example" otherprops="examples"><title>Example</title>
            <p>The following code sample shows how an author provided
        informal information about how to grow a flower from seed:</p><codeblock>&lt;task id="growing-flower>
  &lt;title>Growing a flower from seed&lt;/title>
  &lt;taskbody>
    <b>&lt;steps-informal></b>
      &lt;p>Put the soil in the container any old way. It doesn't really 
         matter how you do it as long as it is at least 12 cm deep. Once 
         the soil is in place, plant the seeds, water appropriately and 
         wait.&lt;/p>
    <b>&lt;/steps-informal></b>
  &lt;/taskbody>
&lt;/task></codeblock></example>
